create_issue "Implement wipe_ledger_state_preserving_modules on SimHost" "Reset host storage while preserving module cache.\n\n**Acceptance criteria:**\n- Storage cleared\n- Module cache preserved\n- Host executable after wipe\n- Test verifies state gone but modules intact" "core,soroban"
create_issue "Implement SourceMapper for WASM offset to source location mapping" "Read DWARF debug info and map byte offsets to source file/line.\n\n**Acceptance criteria:**\n- \`map_wasm_offset_to_source(offset) -> Option<SourceLocation>\`\n- Returns None without debug symbols\n- Test with WASM with and without debug info" "core,wasm"
create_issue "Implement panic-safe execution wrapper" "Wrap contract execution in \`std::panic::catch_unwind\`.\n\n**Acceptance criteria:**\n- Panics caught and returned as errors\n- Simulator does not crash\n- Error includes panic message\n- Test with contract that panics" "core,soroban,security"
